headline: Kari Lake Explains Her Border Plan Is Tougher Than Texas, Savages Karrin
author: Garret Lewis
sentences: Arizona Gubernatorial Kari Lake didn't hold back saying Biden shouldn't be in office, won't listen to what he says about the border, her plan is tougher than the Texas border plan, Karrin Taylor-Robson is Ducey in a skirt, open borders globalist.
